snippet.title: PSX Longplay [176] Speed Punks
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Stenio Henrique

Fun racing game with several characters to play. Reminds me of Mario Kart and the gameplay is good. Just do not have good soundtrack :( but the rest deserve note 10. -
